{
  "stem": "12882.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So it was all written down when he died.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The only thing which was a lie, how he died.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, I was in camp, and I was in a working group which built a-- a-- a system which would lug all kinds of parts through the entire factory.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Was about, well, 30, 40 feet above the ground.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I was hanging up there holding a counterweight to a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was a Dutch citizen, and he was professional [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I was not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And my counter weight wasn't very much at that moment, and it was cold.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I had no gloves, and I had nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I was scared sitting up there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I only said, if I fall down, it's not my fault.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I didn't want to sit there in the first place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "One comes with all kinds of silly ideas.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Well, it didn't last very long, and I got as sick as my brother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I landed up in the Krankenbau, you know, in the hospital section.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they one thing we feared all our life in camp is selection.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "The minute you were not of any value as far as work is concerned to the Germans, they did away with you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They had planned it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So I was sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I was in a selection, and I knew was what happened to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Next morning, I would be brought to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And further on to Birkenau and gassed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Well, in the Krankenbau in Auschwitz, a prison doctor, also a Jew, came around and saw that I was awake at night and started conversation with me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "He said, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] cheer up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "It will be better.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Won't be better.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "This is the end.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I know what gives here.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
